===Background===
===[[Season 2]]===
[[File:Shae threatens.jpg|thumb|Shae holds a knife to the throat of the handmaid in &quot;[[A Man Without Honor]]&quot;.]]
She is a handmaiden to [[Sansa Stark]]. She finds Sansa and [[Shae]] trying to turn over her mattress to conceal Sansa's first [[flowering]]. She attempts to inform Queen [[Cersei Lannister|Cersei]] but Shae threatens her with a knife to keep quiet. Nevertheless, the Queen is informed by [[Sandor Clegane]].&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[A Man Without Honor]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;

===[[Season 3]]===
The handmaiden continues to be assigned to Sansa. She announces [[Tyrion Lannister]] when he calls on Sansa to &quot;propose&quot; to her.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[The Climb]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;

===[[Season 4]]===

The handmaiden continues to spy on Tyrion for Cersei, and discovers that his real secret lover is actually Shae. She then enters Cersei's chambers, while Jaime is present, to inform her of something &quot;important&quot;.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Two Swords]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;
